tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE model_performance_metrics (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    accuracy FLOAT NOT NULL,
    precision FLOAT NOT NULL,
    recall FLOAT NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE model_performance_history (
    history_id SERIAL,
    model_id INT,
    metric_name VARCHAR(50),
    metric_value FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE model_history (
    model_id INT,
    metric_name VARCHAR(255),
    metric_value DECIMAL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    updated_by VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE model_performance_metrics (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    accuracy DECIMAL,
    precision DECIMAL,
    recall DECIMAL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE training_data (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id UUID REFERENCES model_performance_metrics(id),
    feature_1 VARCHAR,
    feature_2 VARCHAR,
    feature_3 VARCHAR,
    feature_4 VARCHAR,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE evaluation_metrics (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id UUID REFERENCES model_performance_metrics(id),
    metric_type VARCHAR,
    metric_value DECIMAL,
    evaluation_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE model_versions (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id UUID REFERENCES model_performance_metrics(id),
    version_number INT,
    deployment_date TIMESTAMP,
    deployed_by VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE model_performance_metrics (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    metric_name VARCHAR(255),
    metric_value DECIMAL(10,2),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE model_history (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    date DATE,
    accuracy DECIMAL(10,2),
    loss DECIMAL(10,2)
)

CREATE TABLE model_training_log (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    epoch_number INT,
    training_loss DECIMAL(10,2),
    validation_loss DECIMAL(10,2),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE model_evaluation_results (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    evaluation_date DATE,
    precision DECIMAL(10,2),
    recall DECIMAL(10,2),
    f1_score DECIMAL(10,2)
)

CREATE TABLE model_metadata (
    metadata_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    description TEXT,
    created_date DATE,
    modified_date DATE
)
